### get-add-service-principal-audits.http
### Author: Shannon Eldridge-Kuehn
### Created: 2026-04-12
### Description: REST example for retrieving Add service principal audit events.

GET https://graph.microsoft.com/v1.0/auditLogs/directoryAudits?$filter=activityDisplayName eq 'Add service principal'
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
